   <--( Game Info )----------------------------------------------- ----- -->
    
    Atelier Ryza: Ever Darkness & the Secret Hideout begins an all-new 
    storyline arc in Gust Studios fan-favourite Atelier series. 

    The beautiful role-playing game follows the exploits of teenage tomboy
    Ryza, who dreams of escaping her mundane village lifestyle alongside 
    her band of mischievous friends. One day, as they explore a forbidden
    island in search of adventure, they meet an elderly magician who will
    change their lives forever. 

    After some convincing, the old man begins teaching Ryza the enchanting
    ways of alchemy, launching her on an adventure that will ultimately 
    lead her on a quest to save her hometown from the mysterious and 
    deadly darkness lurking beneath the surface.

    Features:
    - Join Ryza, and her band of mischievous friends, as they set out to
